{"tid":1797323,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「POPO TG賀聖誕」登上多間外媒國際頭版  果然全亞洲最優秀","createTime":"2019-12-25T10:18:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-25T16:43:52.000Z","uid":212626,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a286619e3162551e86a1ed200a28fa9964350bfc","tid":1797323,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T10:18:50.000Z","msg":"噚晚平安夜，有市民發起「和你Shop」行動，各區多個商場都有大批市民聚集，部分商場爆發警民衝突。其後示威蔓延至街頭，警方一度施放催淚彈驅散人群，多名市民受傷及被捕。<br />\n<br />\n結果今日，外國多間媒體都將「香港平安夜」事件登上國際頭版，報導內容指防暴警察衝入商場用警棍追打示威者，亦用鎗指向人群。報導亦強調當時街上有好多父母同小朋友睇緊燈飾，而警方依然繼續不斷施放催淚彈。<br />\n<br />\n睇返歷史，喺第一次世界大戰期間，德國同英、法軍隊曾經於平安夜同聖誕節達成一個非官方嘅短暫休戰協議（當時休戰協議書被各國官方拒絕，但士兵自己選擇休戰）。而鍾意講「國際標準」、自稱全亞洲最優秀嘅香港POPO，噚晚就選擇用TG為香港市民帶嚟白色聖誕。瘋狂得咁合乎國際標準，難怪上晒國際頭版。<br />\n<br />\n原圖來源：BBC, New York Times, France24, The Guardian, The Telegraph<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BAwcd79.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBAwcd79.png&h=79d51eb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89beb375e4a8ffa8fbd1034e76edcdfcc72fa441","tid":1797323,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T10:21:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71d429a4e4c87b09f030273275baf17644e6cc9b","tid":1797323,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T10:34:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab6edeecf25c368ff3e8f08ab926bba5713feb11","tid":1797323,"uid":34816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T10:35:06.000Z","msg":"亞洲第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"427af61ff10808422c71d2240dcb2b094ebeeb36","tid":1797323,"uid":226984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T10:50:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f77609215e07a1476f594392c89c4a7762262432","tid":1797323,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T14:48:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"320ad4fdd4bd1f7ec55c2e2f1e6ada018c94744e","tid":1797323,"uid":58841,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T16:40:04.000Z","msg":"歷史睇返戰爭成點都會係聖誕期間休戰<br />\n得班狗先至咁癲平安夜都要搞搞震<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n俾無腦又容易失控既狗揸槍就係咁既下場"},{"pid":"07945d3203d5ff9aaf892e6389de66abdf5b638a","tid":1797323,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T16:41:41.000Z","msg":"【第拾玖期牆紙】毋懼強權<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1797162/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1797162/page/1</a><br />\nTG : <a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=TvOq0m68uPCtaVYdNLQuFFYPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=c1726810\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperENews</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nqcF6Fe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnqcF6Fe.jpg&h=44c58009&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"07106982ebf817ebf634a4aeaff6b8261224e6bd","tid":1797323,"uid":35087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T16:42:16.000Z","msg":"亞洲第一垃圾"},{"pid":"de070117d0339dcf9adc4d054fe2bf508bdff4c6","tid":1797323,"uid":36152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T16:43:37.000Z","msg":"唔係全亞洲，係衝出全球，"},{"pid":"6f7f8c7e1cafb0864de2f45b0572119a44275927","tid":1797323,"uid":14601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T16:43:41.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"48baa1215533d502360ffed10c04881629b5310c"